1979 beating against a terrible storm off a lee coast of black rocks and
1980 snowy breakers.  But high above the flying scud and dark-rolling
1981 clouds, there floated a little isle of sunlight, from which beamed
1982 forth an angel's face; and this bright face shed a distinct spot of
1983 radiance upon the ship's tossed deck, something like that silver
