1989 Nor was the pulpit itself without a trace of the same sea-taste that
1990 had achieved the ladder and the picture.  Its panelled front was in
1991 the likeness of a ship's bluff bows, and the Holy Bible rested on a
1992 projecting piece of scroll work, fashioned after a ship's
1993 fiddle-headed beak.
