1995 What could be more full of meaning?--for the pulpit is ever this
1996 earth's foremost part; all the rest comes in its rear; the pulpit
1997 leads the world.  From thence it is the storm of God's quick wrath is
1998 first descried, and the bow must bear the earliest brunt.  From
1999 thence it is the God of breezes fair or foul is first invoked for
2000 favourable winds.  Yes, the world's a ship on its passage out, and not
2001 a voyage complete; and the pulpit is its prow.
