2269 While he was speaking these words, the howling of the shrieking,
2270 slanting storm without seemed to add new power to the preacher, who,
2271 when describing Jonah's sea-storm, seemed tossed by a storm himself.
2272 His deep chest heaved as with a ground-swell; his tossed arms seemed
