3141 circle of these slabs laced together, mutually sloped towards each
3142 other, and at the apex united in a tufted point, where the loose
3143 hairy fibres waved to and fro like the top-knot on some old
3144 Pottowottamie Sachem's head.  A triangular opening faced towards the
