7494 One of the wild suggestions referred to, as at last coming to be
7495 linked with the White Whale in the minds of the superstitiously
7496 inclined, was the unearthly conceit that Moby Dick was ubiquitous;
7497 that he had actually been encountered in opposite latitudes at one
7498 and the same instant of time.
