8037 Tell me, why this strong young colt, foaled in some peaceful valley
8038 of Vermont, far removed from all beasts of prey--why is it that upon
8039 the sunniest day, if you but shake a fresh buffalo robe behind him,
8040 so that he cannot even see it, but only smells its wild animal
8041 muskiness--why will he start, snort, and with bursting eyes paw the
8042 ground in phrensies of affright?  There is no remembrance in him of
8043 any gorings of wild creatures in his green northern home, so that the
8044 strange muskiness he smells cannot recall to him anything associated
8045 with the experience of former perils; for what knows he, this New
8046 England colt, of the black bisons of distant Oregon?
8047 
8048 No; but here thou beholdest even in a dumb brute, the instinct of the
8049 knowledge of the demonism in the world.  Though thousands of miles
8050 from Oregon, still when he smells that savage musk, the rending,
8051 goring bison herds are as present as to the deserted wild foal of the
8052 prairies, which this instant they may be trampling into dust.
8053 
8054 Thus, then, the muffled rollings of a milky sea; the bleak rustlings
8055 of the festooned frosts of mountains; the desolate shiftings of the
8056 windrowed snows of prairies; all these, to Ishmael, are as the
8057 shaking of that buffalo robe to the frightened colt!
8058 
8059 Though neither knows where lie the nameless things of which the
8060 mystic sign gives forth such hints; yet with me, as with the colt,
8061 somewhere those things must exist.  Though in many of its aspects
8062 this visible world seems formed in love, the invisible spheres were
8063 formed in fright.
8064 
8065 But not yet have we solved the incantation of this whiteness, and
8066 learned why it appeals with such power to the soul; and more strange
8067 and far more portentous--why, as we have seen, it is at once the most
8068 meaning symbol of spiritual things, nay, the very veil of the
8069 Christian's Deity; and yet should be as it is, the intensifying agent
8070 in things the most appalling to mankind.
