9567 rigging, and hailed the mortal crew.  "There she blows!"  Had the
9568 trump of judgment blown, they could not have quivered more; yet still
9569 they felt no terror; rather pleasure.  For though it was a most
9570 unwonted hour, yet so impressive was the cry, and so deliriously
9571 exciting, that almost every soul on board instinctively desired a
9572 lowering.
