14438 know--relieve distressed travellers.  Hurrah! this is the way to sail
14439 now.  Every keel a sunbeam!  Hurrah!--Here we go like three tin
14440 kettles at the tail of a mad cougar!  This puts me in mind of
14441 fastening to an elephant in a tilbury on a plain--makes the
14442 wheel-spokes fly, boys, when you fasten to him that way; and there's
