16052 A common man looking at this decision of the very learned Judge,
16053 might possibly object to it.  But ploughed up to the primary rock of
16054 the matter, the two great principles laid down in the twin whaling
16055 laws previously quoted, and applied and elucidated by Lord
16056 Ellenborough in the above cited case; these two laws touching
