16212 Greenland or Right whale was largely used in ladies' bodices.  But
16213 this same bone is not in the tail; it is in the head, which is a sad
16214 mistake for a sagacious lawyer like Prynne.  But is the Queen a
16215 mermaid, to be presented with a tail?  An allegorical meaning may
16216 lurk here.
