16837 Would that I could keep squeezing that sperm for ever!  For now,
16838 since by many prolonged, repeated experiences, I have perceived that
16839 in all cases man must eventually lower, or at least shift, his
16840 conceit of attainable felicity; not placing it anywhere in the
16841 intellect or the fancy; but in the wife, the heart, the bed, the
