16873 There is another substance, and a very singular one, which turns up
16874 in the course of this business, but which I feel it to be very
16875 puzzling adequately to describe.  It is called slobgollion; an
16876 appellation original with the whalemen, and even so is the nature of
16877 the substance.  It is an ineffably oozy, stringy affair, most
16878 frequently found in the tubs of sperm, after a prolonged squeezing,
